Crawler - HowTo

Parameters
Value	What		Value						Type				Example			Required
-u	URL		Enter URL					String **Required		www.google.com		Yes
-c	No Of Links	No Of Links To Be Crawled			Integer [Default Unlimited]	10			Optional
-e	Crawling Mode	1 - Internal Crawling.	0 - External [Default]	Integer	[Default 0]		1			Optional

Basic Usage

python filename.py -u domainname

Example Usages

python filename.py -u www.google.com

python filename.py -u www.google.com -c 10 -e 1

python filename.py -u mysite.com -c 10 -e 0
